ichkeit besonders intensiv verhandelt. Ihre Analyse der einzelnen Starfiguren fügt Antje Dechert zu einer Körpergeschichte Italiens zwischen Faschismus und 68er-Bewegung zusammen.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 30. Aug 2021) 7aART / General.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Arts and Architecture 2014z9783110369595oZDB-23-DKA08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Complete Package 2014z9783110369526oZDB-23-DGG40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783412218003423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9783412218003.jpg  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-DGGb2014  aZDB-23-DKAb2014